snippet.title: Mr.Timan Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is a walkthrough of the game "Mr.Timan".

Play the game here: http://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/676854

You can visit my Patreon page if you want or something:
https://www.patreon.com/awalkthroughlife

Game created by Vogd3
___________
Game description (from creator):
The game was made in a week for ID.net+Y8.com Game Contest - March 2016. (Graphics was improved later)
Play as Mr.Timan - a new employee in Time Company. All what you need is press red button. But may be this was not a good idea. 
Physics platformer with time-portals. One place - two times and different level geometry. Enjoy!
___________
#walkthrough
